        <para>Tamboti runs with recent versions of all major browsers: </para>
        <itemizedlist>
            <ulink href="http://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/new/">
                <listitem>Firefox</listitem>
            </ulink>
            <ulink href="http://www.apple.com/safari/download/">
                <listitem>Safari</listitem>
            </ulink>
            <ulink href="https://www.google.com/chrome/?hl=en&amp;brand=chmo">
                <listitem>Chrome</listitem>
            </ulink>
            <ulink href="http://www.microsoft.com/download/en/details.aspx?id=13950">
                <listitem>Internet Explorer 9</listitem>
            </ulink>
            <ulink href="http://www.opera.com/browser/download/">
                <listitem>Opera</listitem>
            </ulink>
        </itemizedlist>
        <para>The Tamboti search interface does not work with Internet Explorer 6 and 7. The Tamboti
            editor does not work with Internet Explorer 6, 7, and 8. Note that this means that if
            you are running Windows XP, you cannot use Internet Explorer to access Tamboti fully.
            You may, however, use Internet Explorer 8 to <emphasis>search</emphasis> Tamboti.</para>
        <para>Please note that since late 2011, most browsers have accellerated their update cycle.
            This may create problems with breaking browser versions, especially from development
            branches, since they are not always thoroughly tested. If you run into a problem, please
            let us know.</para>
